Usage: eco_opt_ir_aggressor [-help] [-create_margin] -domain_threshold <float>
                            [-effort <string>] [-margin <float>] [-noEcoRoute]
                            [-save_margin] [-single_iter]
                            -state_directory <string> [-watch_box <string>]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-create_margin                # whether create margin for uncommits
                              # (bool, optional)
-domain_threshold <float>     # domain threshold (float, required)
-effort <string>              # effort level high||medium||low
                              # (string, optional)
-margin <float>               # how many nano seconds to create
                              # (float, optional)
-noEcoRoute                   # don't do ecoRoute in the end (bool, optional)
-save_margin                  # saves margin for the next run of ireco
                              # (bool, optional)
-single_iter                  # only run the 1st iteration with margin creation
                              # (bool, optional)
-state_directory <string>     # state_directory (string, required)
-watch_box <string>           # only the violations inside the box will be calc
                              # (string, optional)